tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE partnership (
  partnership_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  philanthropic_entity_id INT,
  government_agency_id INT,
  partnership_start_date DATE,
  partnership_end_date DATE,
  partnership_description TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE philanthropic_entities (
  entity_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  entity_name VARCHAR(255),
  contact_person VARCHAR(255),
  partnership_description TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE government_agencies (
  agency_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  agency_name VARCHAR(255),
  agency_type VARCHAR(50),
  contact_person VARCHAR(255)
)

CREATE TABLE partnerships (
  partnership_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  entity_id INT,
  agency_id INT,
  start_date DATE,
  end_date DATE,
  partnership_status VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE Partnerships (
    partnership_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    philanthropic_entity_id INT,
    government_agency_id INT,
    partnership_type VARCHAR(50),
    partnership_start_date DATE,
    partnership_end_date DATE,
    CONSTRAINT fk_philanthropic_entity FOREIGN KEY (philanthropic_entity_id) REFERENCES PhilanthropicEntities(entity_id),
    CONSTRAINT fk_government_agency FOREIGN KEY (government_agency_id) REFERENCES GovernmentAgencies(agency_id)
);

CREATE TABLE PhilanthropicEntities (
    entity_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    entity_name VARCHAR(100),
    entity_type VARCHAR(50),
    entity_location VARCHAR(100),
    entity_website VARCHAR(200)
);

CREATE TABLE GovernmentAgencies (
    agency_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    agency_name VARCHAR(100),
    agency_type VARCHAR(50),
    agency_location VARCHAR(100),
    agency_contact_person VARCHAR(100)
);

CREATE TABLE PartnershipDetails (
    detail_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    partnership_id INT,
    detail_description TEXT,
    detail_amount DECIMAL(12, 2),
    detail_date DATE,
    CONSTRAINT fk_partnership FOREIGN KEY (partnership_id) REFERENCES Partnerships(partnership_id)
);

CREATE TABLE partnerships (
    partnership_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    entity_id INT NOT NULL,
    agency_id INT NOT NULL,
    partnership_date DATE,
    partnership_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    FOREIGN KEY (entity_id) REFERENCES philanthropic_entities(entity_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (agency_id) REFERENCES government_agencies(agency_id)
);

CREATE TABLE partnership_funding (
    funding_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    partnership_id INT NOT NULL,
    funding_amount DECIMAL(10, 2) NOT NULL,
    funding_date DATE,
    funding_purpose TEXT,
    FOREIGN KEY (partnership_id) REFERENCES partnerships(partnership_id)
);

CREATE TABLE partnership_reports (
    report_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    partnership_id INT NOT NULL,
    report_date DATE,
    report_details TEXT,
    FOREIGN KEY (partnership_id) REFERENCES partnerships(partnership_id)
);
